the title comes from act iii , scene iii of shakespeare 's play , in which othello declares his love for desdemona , " perdition catch my soul , but i do love thee ; and when i love thee not , chaos is come again . "   although much of the plot remains intact , othello , the " noble moor " becomes the pacifist leader of a hippie commune , iago appears to be the devil incarnate who " fits all the negative stereotypes of dropouts with his scruffy beard and unwashed look " and desdemona becomes a " white round - faced girl with granny glasses " .

shaking up shakespeare : jerry lee lewis did shakespeare ! in 1968 's " catch my soul " , a rock musical based on " othello " , he played this villain

iago